snippet.title: The Sirena Expedition - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sirena Expedition is a 2.5D puzzle-platformer with horror elements, made in the style of a PlayStation1 game. In it you will explore an abandoned facility at the bottom of the Mariana Trench and uncover the secrets buried there.

The game is releasing on Steam and Itch.io on the 26th of October.

Play the demo and wishlist the game here! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1957300/The_Sirena_Expedition/
